Food Fighters US - Season 2, Episode 2




You're in the Big Leagues Now

Holly Haines, a web designer from San Diego, California, puts her Filipino fusion food to the test. She's half-Filipino and half-black and says food really gives her a way to express her love for both cultures. If she wins the $100,000, she'll turn her passion for throwing themed dinners into a full-time pop-up restaurant business.




Original Air Date: 09-Jul-2015
